{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"01538662-0e08-4342-8f07-2f28ebee24a5","content":"No files found in the working directory. I'll provide the solution directly.\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd `x:DataType` to your `ContentPage` to enable compiled bindings:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n\n        <Entry Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" Placeholder=\"Theme\" />\n\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n\n        <Stepper Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\" Minimum=\"8\" Maximum=\"36\" />\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize, StringFormat='Font Size: {0}'}\" />\n\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\n**Key changes:**\n1. Added `xmlns:vm` namespace pointing to your ViewModel namespace.\n2. Added `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` on the root element.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\nAdd this to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <!-- Treat binding failures as build errors -->\n  <MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\nWith `x:DataType` set, the compiler resolves bindings at compile time. If you typo a property (e.g., `{Binding Themee}`), you'll get a **build error** like:\n\n```\nXC0045: Binding: Property \"Themee\" not found on \"SettingsViewModel\"\n```\n\n**Tips:**\n- If you need to opt out for a specific binding (e.g., an ancestor binding), use `x:DataType=\"\"` locally to disable compiled bindings on that element.\n- Compiled bindings also improve runtime performance by avoiding reflection.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"7a95aeaa-5079-4f54-9cd1-6c28cf217f24","outputTokens":516,"requestId":"980D:165513:15D086C:185C1CF:6A051DEF"},"id":"ddaa3f61-d15b-4c99-86e3-d5b605eb6e74","timestamp":"2026-05-14T00:57:30.659Z","parentId":"69942a25-667c-4c90-8708-f36f92398bae"}
